  "signal_description": "Calculate the percentage of completed purchase order items where the last goods receipt creation date is later than the last requested delivery date. The query is performed on the 'defaultview-57' table. The 'case_id' column is used to count the number of cases. The numerator of the calculation is the count of case_id values where the last goods receipt creation date is later than the last requested delivery date and the 'PO Item Delivery Completed' column is set to 'Yes'. The denominator is the count of case_id values where the 'PO Item Delivery Completed' column is set to 'Yes'. The result is multiplied by 100 to obtain the percentage."
